name: Inzektor Picofalena
text:
2 Insect monsters
You can target 3 Insect monsters in your GY; shuffle them into the Deck, then draw 1 card. If this card is Link Summoned: You can discard 1 card, then target 1 other Insect monster you control; equip 1 Insect monster from your Deck to it as an Equip Card with this effect.
â—? The equipped monster gains 500 ATK/DEF.
You can only use each effect of "Inzektor Picofarena" once per turn.
